<!-- DO NOT edit this page or format !!! -->[[Madonna (entertainer)|Madonna]] continues to push the barriers with her music videos. She has worked with many highly successful directors and has produced many music videos that are considered by many as works of art. Her 1995 video to "[[Bedtime Story (Madonna song)|Bedtime Story]]" was acquired for the New York [[MOMA|Museum of Modern Art]]'s permanent film and video collection. Always controversial and sometimes misunderstood, her videos have depicted subjects such as teen pregnancy, religion, sex, and violence.
